WEBVTT

00:10:26.164 --> 00:10:30.439
This is something that designers
also have to deal with frequently.

00:10:32.638 --> 00:10:35.527
My work most recently took me to Haiti.

00:10:36.049 --> 00:10:40.238
Design thinkers often seek out
extreme situations,

00:10:40.262 --> 00:10:44.517
because that often informs
some of their best designs.

00:10:44.541 --> 00:10:47.580
And Haiti -- it was like a perfect storm.

00:10:48.415 --> 00:10:52.822
I lived and worked
with 300 Deaf individuals

00:10:53.656 --> 00:10:56.775
that were relocated
after the 2010 earthquake.

00:10:57.805 --> 00:11:00.971
But five and a half years later,